             Former Cuban President  Fidel Castro 
appeared yesterday at a the celebration of Cubaâ€™s Revolution
Day, government newspaper  Granma  reported.  
 Castro, wearing a green shirt, called for a meeting of
Cuban leaders to discuss foreign affairs, including the U.S.
